after the volume is created 
  attach the vol. to the instance (actions)
 take control
to check
$ lsblk
to check if vol. is raw
$ sudo file -s /dev/xvdf
to format the disk
$ sudo mkfs -t ext4 /dev/xvdf
check again  $ sudo file -s /dev/xvdf
 # create mount point for the disk
 $ sudo mkdir </fileserver>
now mount the disk
$ sudo mount /dev/xvdf /fileserver/
check $ lsblk
to go in drive $ cd /fileserver
to unmount the disk
$ sudo umount /dev/xvdf /fileserver
check $ lsblk
deattach the vol. from instance
 
